WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.666 --> 00:00:01.833
Has the fever gone?

2
00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:06.466
Don't eat it.

3
00:00:06.466 --> 00:00:08.200
I said don't touch me

4
00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:11.066
Mr. Shen, it was enough for me last time

5
00:00:12.966 --> 00:00:14.266
I didn't lie to you.

6
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:15.600
at least

7
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.433
I mean it all the time.

8
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:22.633
The more you touch him

9
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:27.066
The more it hurts to think

10
00:00:29.133 --> 00:00:30.600
Fall in love with a substitute

11
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:32.000
It's ironic

12
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.433
How do you know that?

13
00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:36.366
Shen Tinglan, let me tell you

14
00:00:37.066 --> 00:00:39.866
I hate it when people take me for a fool

15
00:00:40.266 --> 00:00:41.633
I ask you once

16
00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:44.966
Are you true to me or to him?

17
00:00:46.166 --> 00:00:46.966
at that time

18
00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:55.100
wait

19
00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:08.400
I'm hurt.

20
00:01:08.866 --> 00:01:10.066
Take Me Home

21
00:01:10.366 --> 00:01:13.300
But I love him

22
00:01:15.466 --> 00:01:17.700
More than anyone else in the world

